<ul>
  <li>Deep learning models for elucidating the architectures of transcription regulation networks.</li>
  <li>Bayesian hierarchical models for identification of trait-associated genes for major depressive disorder patients.</li>
  <li>A Django web application for predicting genetic mutation deleteriousness by ensemble learning.</li>
</ul>

